➜挺“秃”然的！我国超2.5亿人受脱发困扰，过半数植发者是90后
http://www.sohu.com/a/437272975_162758	42468
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
